searchParameters.q: how much are original cabbage patch dolls worth

answerBox.snippet: Cabbage Patch Kid dolls vary in price depending on their condition, but the average doll can sell for $20 to $500, and many have sold for at least $100. The value of a doll can increase from hundreds of dollars to thousands if its original box, body, clothes, adoption papers, and birth certificate are intact.

peopleAlsoAsk.question: Why are Cabbage Patch Kids so expensive?
peopleAlsoAsk.snippet: If demand exceeds supply, prices rise. Back in the 80's, toy stores couldn't keep Cabbage Patch Kids in stock, so the price rose. Black markets sprung up because individuals wanted to capitalize on the inflated prices which were made worse by further limited supply.
